Awonder Liang vs Vassily Ivanchuk
Sunway Sitges International (2019), Round 8
Reti opening (A04)

1. Nf3 d6 2. d4 Nf6 3. g3 g6 4. Bg2 Bg7 5. O-O O-O 6. Re1 Nbd7 7. e4 e5 8. Nc3 b6 9. Nd5 Nxd5 10. exd5 Re8 11. c3 a5 12. h4 Ba6 13. h5 exd4 14. h6 Rxe1+ 15. Qxe1 Bf6 16. Nxd4 Ne5 17. Be3 Qd7 18. Nc6 Nxc6 19. dxc6 Qf5 20. Rd1 Re8 21. Qd2 Qe5 22. Qc2 Qh5 23. Rd5 Re5 24. Qb3 Kf8 25. Rxe5 Qxe5 26. Bxb6 cxb6 27. Qxb6 Qb5 28. Qa7 Bg5 29. c7 Qc5 30. Qb8+ Ke7 31. Bb7

The 6th Sunway Sitges International is a 10-round Swiss open taking place from 13-22 December 2019 in the Hotel Sunway Playa Golf & Spa in Sitges, Spain.

Players receive 90 minutes for 40 moves, followed by 30 minutes to the end of the game, plus a 30-second increment starting from move one. Official website: www.sunwaychessfestival.com
